Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBModule

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBModule
public class JDBModule
extends java.lang.Object
The JDBModule is used to insert/update/delete records in the SYS_MODULES table. The modules database contains a definition of all screens/reports and functions available within the application. These modules are assigned to groups and groups are assigned to users.

See Also:
JDBGroupPermissions
